        <p class="TableTextEmphasis">mc-breadcrumbs-count</p>
        <p class="TableText">Determines the number of breadcrumbs to show (i.e., how many levels of file and folder names you wish to display from the TOC). For example, the default setting is 3, so 3 breadcrumbs would appear in the following manner: You are here: First Topic &gt; Second Topic &gt; Third Topic.</p>
        <p class="TableText" MadCap:conditions="General.Online-Only">
            <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Flare/Proxies/Breadcrumbs/Editing-Look-Breadcrumbs.htm">Using Styles to Determine the Look of Breadcrumbs</MadCap:xref>
        </p>
    </body>
</html>